OL,3,CMan who failed to comply with
OL,4,Cflytipping investigation fined #1400
OL,6,FA man has been fined in connection
OL,7,Fwith fly-tipping in Andover.
OL,9,FRubbish dumped on Watery Lane led
OL,10,Fcouncil officers to Oliver Poulton.
OL,12,FHe failed to show up on two occasions
OL,13,Ffor an interview under caution -
OL,14,Fdespite being served a formal notice.
OL,16,FPoulton has been ordered to pay back
OL,17,Fmore than #1400.
