OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772025560
OL,3,CMan who failed to comply with
OL,4,Cflytipping investigation fined #1400
OL,6,FCouncillor David Drew, portfolio
OL,7,Fholder for recycling and environmental
OL,8,Fservices at Test Valley Borough
OL,9,FCouncil, said: "When people choose not
OL,10,Fto engage with our investigations, it
OL,11,Fslows us down and puts extra pressure
OL,12,Fon the teams who work hard to protect
OL,13,Four environment.
OL,15,F"Fly tipping and the issues linked to
OL,16,Fit impact everyone.
OL,18,F"We rely on residents to cooperate so
OL,19,Fwe can gather the facts quickly and
OL,20,Fdeal with offences fairly and
OL,21,Feffectively.
OL,26,@qD@POU
