PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772025560
OL,3,CMan who failed to comply with
OL,4,Cflytipping investigation fined #1400
OL,6,F"Our communities expect us to tackle
OL,7,Fwaste crime, and cases like this show
OL,8,Fthat we'll continue to follow through
OL,9,Fwhen someone doesn't meet their
OL,10,Fresponsibilities.
OL,12,F"We want Test Valley to remain a
OL,13,Fclean, safe and welcoming place, and
OL,14,Fwe'll keep taking firm but fair action
OL,15,Fto make sure that happens."
